Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.07,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Allow me to give you a metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.80,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Much like this exquisite rose,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:23.12,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,your beauty has only just begun to bloom. {Doing a little experimenting so we don't use as many ellipsis}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.68,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But consider this, Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:32.22,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Once a flower has bloomed, \Nall that remains for it is to wither away and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.50,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Such a pity, isn't it?
