Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.23,Main,Dire,0,0,0,,He even managed to squeeze out the venom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:54.29,Main,Dire,0,0,0,,It's amazing he gained such control over \Nthe flow of his blood in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:59.58,Main,Speedwagon,0,0,0,,It's because old man Zeppeli passed his \Nlife force on to Mr. Joestar before he died!
