Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:16.00,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Dio... let me tell you how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.81,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,Although it is unbecoming of a gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.56,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,To be perfectly honest, right now I, Jonathan Joestar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.70,Main,Jonathan,0,0,0,,...would like nothing more than to avenge\N the people you've killed, Dio! Prepare to die!
